attributionInfo.brokerName: Keller Williams Premier Realty Lake Minnetonka

data.description: Welcome to this great property located in the popular Beachside community. Walk to Shady Oak Lake and beach, Lone Lake Park and the regional walking/biking trail! Convenient to nearby shopping and transit! Features include vault ceilings, a spacious floor plan, open Kitchen and Breakfast area, Formal Dining Room, spacious Primary Bedroom with a private bath and walk-in closet, a nice deck overlooking the yard, finished Family Room in the lower walkout level, brick fireplace and an oversize garage. The property is ready for a light refresh - Carpet & paint - and other upgrades as mechanicals are up to date and kitchen cabinetry has been replaced.
